{"tid":624054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下學期測驗前夕　青衣中二女生校園墮樓","createTime":"2018-04-10T13:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T14:10:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"807858eaa5eea86e496abf788439dc7afc7800ed","tid":624054,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/photo/bkn-20180410180226984-0410_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180410203748\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180410180226984-0410_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180410203748&h=f8a2bddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青衣一學校有女生墮樓受傷。現場為牙鷹洲街12號中華基督教燕京書院，據悉，下午5時54分，一名14歲中二女生在上址2樓墮下受傷，救護員接報趕抵，將女生送院，她神志仍清醒。警方正調查事件原因。據了解，女生盆骨有少許碎裂，幸無生命危險；她最近沒就學業問題向校方求助。 <br />\n<br />\n中華基督教燕京書院發言人稱，今天放學後約下午5時30分，一名中二女生從學校2樓樓梯墮下，她清醒能清楚告訴自己姓名和班別。學校立即致電999及家長，並由社工及輔導主任陪同女生送院。 <br />\n<br />\n發言人續稱，明天是學校下學期統一測驗第一天，女生成績中上，一向對學業有要求。校方感恩，獲悉女生經急症室醫生診斷後，證實並無大礙，校方會繼續與家長保持溝通，校長今晚會到醫院探望女生，表達慰問。校方已成立危機處理小組，商討支援措施。發言人強調，校方一向關注學生的身心需要，會繼續密切留意師生的需要，提供適切的支援。校方明天將會通知全體師生，為受傷女生祈禱。"},{"pid":"04bcb2e41cf955d7e380162ebe2c3133b40a8dc5","tid":624054,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"好彩住二樓"},{"pid":"b304f49eee5b3ba5f98b52ab87a7ef8fd4fb557a","tid":624054,"uid":105462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04bcb2e41cf955d7e380162ebe2c3133b40a8dc5","tid":624054,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"好彩住二樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf45db5fdcd2880665a440c631904e8851c0227","tid":624054,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩住二樓</blockquote><br />\n中二就梗係住二樓"},{"pid":"cb3da01f4db7fc4077e58ce3a37063389b7c9e03","tid":624054,"uid":87780,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"校方明天將會通知全體師生，為受傷女生祈禱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6744a3a6eb0115b0649c18963318da30456f6632","tid":624054,"uid":15410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"間學校想個女仔變成全校笑柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46788bd64bb4dd570beaab199079961e64c190cd","tid":624054,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb3da01f4db7fc4077e58ce3a37063389b7c9e03","tid":624054,"uid":87780,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"校方明天將會通知全體師生，為受傷女生祈禱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"耶撚有咩問題唔係靠自己<br />\n乜都叫主搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3317cc8c4e613a3e7f9d6c4efaa2024a7385fc3f","tid":624054,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"2樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261eed624001c597f66fa4c5c076c9a698a7d076","tid":624054,"uid":62192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"唔死得，可以繼續返學校考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />